alt_text: Cyberg Sam, the Christmas 2021 skin variant from Roblox game Bear* wearing a Christmas hat and appearing to have a left robotic eye patch with a red glowing eye, the other being a normal yet angry face, his left leg is robotic as well. Holding a candy cane in his right arm and his left robotic arm grasping nothing in a half-clenched fist. he wears a strap around his chest that have lightbulbs attached, a cape with a pink and blue orb that serves as a button to keep the cape together, inside of cape is a galaxy-like design inside. 1 blue and 1 pink eye can be seen behind sam with the pink being a little offscreen, the lines have a dark red color on them with a half cyan blue and half bright pink around the character art. A dark blue mixed with green background is distorted in a  way that makes everything behind look wavy.
